<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-08-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-08-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="311" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d311">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Pedro Montt</persName>
                                to Mr. <persName type="to">Blaine</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the Constitutional Government of
                                    Chile</hi>,<lb/>1325 <hi rend="smallcaps">G Street
                                        NW</hi>.,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>,
                                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-08-28"><hi rend="italic">August 28, 1891</hi>.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I am directed by the minister of foreign
                            affairs to lay before the Government of the United States the following
                            cablegram: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p rend="center">[Translation.]</p>
                                <p>Balmaceda has been routed for the second time. To-day, after the
                                    victory of the congressional forces outside of the city,
                                    Valparaiso was surrendered to the German admiral, who placed it
                                    under the orders of Congress. Inform Government.</p>
                                <p rend="right"><hi rend="smallcaps">Errazuriz</hi>.</p>
                                <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Iquique</hi>, <hi rend="italic">August 28,
                                        1891</hi>.</p>
                            </quote></p>
                        <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                        <closer><signed>
                                <list>
                                    <item><hi rend="smallcaps">Pedro Montt</hi>.</item>
                                    <item>Per <hi rend="smallcaps">Julio M. Foster</hi>.</item>
                                </list>
                            </signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>